Upgrading from version 2.8.(2-3) to 2.8.4

1. install SQL-Ledger over top
   # cd /usr/local
   # tar zxvf sql-ledger-2.8.4.tar.gz

2. fix permissions
   # chown -hR nobody:nogroup *
   # chmod 711 templates users css spool

Note: replace nobody:nogroup with your web server user and group

3. copy the following files without the Default- prefix to
   your private template directory
   
   Default-remittance_voucher.tex
   Default-remittance_voucher.html

4. log in

